盖茨比，她的未来有没有可能变得更好呢（其实我自认为也不会但是有没有这种可能呢），是怎样的时代背景与生活环境促使她做出这样的选择，她的做法对于盖茨比来说是否太残忍了些，她自己会这样认为吗，会后悔吗？如果后悔的话是后悔当初没有选择盖茨比，还是后悔将撞人逃逸嫁祸于盖茨比、并且直到盖茨比的葬礼她都没有现身？ 感觉越说越乱了哈哈哈，想知道大家对于黛西的解读与看法，说不定能从中收获很多，也欢迎大家一起讨论，谢谢！"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ig5np7f6hluxREAMaCDY1NDY4Mzg5IMy5iIYGMAY4+gdAGnIJNDY0MzQ5NzQ4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"86 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picb.zhimg.com/50/v2-cce177e4773b756aa0145ef7a13678e8_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"27_1624115151.1929214","card_id":"Q_461105913","target":{"id":461105913,"title":"你会选择和一个你不喜欢但喜欢你的人过一辈子还是一个人过一辈子?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/461105913","type":"question","created":1621822706,"answer_count":355,"follower_count":444,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[126120,181694,187293],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Ig5np7f6hluxREAMaCDY0NzQ3NjQ5IPKZrIUGMAE4vANAG3IJNDYxMTA1OTEzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"81 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-207c5f211f20036ef94bc2b1821c90b4_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"28_1624115151.1932135","card_id":"Q_464776360","target":{"id":464776360,"title":"大家能给我讲一个笑话吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/464776360","type":"question","created":1623563211,"answer_count":26,"follower_count":48,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4447,4453,95644],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"太累了，心烦，迷茫"},"attached_info":"Cj4Ig5np7f6hluxREAMaCDY1NTYzMTAyIMu3loYGMAA4MEAccgk0NjQ3NzYzNjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"73 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thum